label: Complexity Of Process
definition: Justification that the process is delayed due to complexity in fulfilling it

label: High Volume Of Processes
definition: Justification that the process is delayed due to high volume of similar processes required to be fulfilled

label: Identity Verification Required
definition: Justification that the process could not be fulfilled or was not successful because identity verification is required

label: Information Required
definition: Justification that the process is delayed due to additional information being required
